rows.label: qst500201_msg0001
rows.name:
Friend very unusual to come all way
out here and talk to Foorara.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0002
rows.name:
Foorara was not trying to do
anything dangerous, especially.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0003
rows.name:
When Nopon born in Voltis Trade Guild
become five years old, must go out
alone for initiation called Walky-Walky.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0004
rows.name:
First stop on journey is Goldmund.
Foorara must have a look at work of
fellow Nopon at Avaritia Trade Guild.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0005
rows.name:
So Foorara was studying very
closely activities of salvagers
at unfamiliar guild.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0006
rows.name:
But thought of that amount of hard
work make Foorara not want to
become grown up.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0007
rows.name:
Voltis Trade Guild Walky-Walky Guide
Book say, when Walky-Walky Nopon
become sad, time to move on.

rows.label: qst500201_msg0008
rows.name:
Next go to place with wonderful view,
get fresh feeling and forget sad things!

rows.label: qst500201_msg0009
rows.name:
Maybe Foorara destined to meet friend
again. Best of luck!
